OL,3,CMore protection for blind people from
OL,4,Cpolice impersonators
OL,6,FITV News' Sam Taylor spoke to blind
OL,7,Fand visually impaired people to find
OL,8,Fout how the new plan aims to keep them
OL,9,Fsafe.
OL,11,FA police force has introduced a new
OL,12,Fplan which aims to protect blind and
OL,13,Fvisually impaired people from
OL,14,Ffraudsters who pose as officers.
OL,16,FWhile most people can rely on an
OL,17,Fofficer's uniform or their collar
OL,18,Fnumber to confirm their identity,
OL,19,Fblind and visually impaired people are
OL,20,Foften unable to use these methods.
