OL,3,CMore protection for blind people from
OL,4,Cpolice impersonators
OL,6,FInstead, Greater Manchester Police's
OL,7,FVisual Impairment Protocol (VIP)
OL,8,Fallows them to call the non-emergency
OL,9,Fline and confirm an officer has been
OL,10,Fsent to their address.
OL,12,FFor Colin Adamson, who is severely
OL,13,Fsight impaired, a knock at the door
OL,14,Fcan often be "a source of dread".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
