OL,3,CMore protection for blind people from
OL,4,Cpolice impersonators
OL,6,FHe said: "You know you're home and
OL,7,Fyou're safe when you're in your
OL,8,Fproperty... But when someone knocks at
OL,9,Fyour door it's like letting that
OL,10,Fbarrier down and if you don't know who
OL,11,Fthey are you need to be able to trust
OL,12,Fthem."
OL,14,FColin is just one of 16,000 people in
OL,15,FGreater Manchester living with a
OL,16,Fvisual impairment, which includes
OL,17,Fblindness and partial sight loss.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
