OL,3,CMore protection for blind people from
OL,4,Cpolice impersonators
OL,6,FIt's hoped the new plan will make
OL,7,Fblind and visually impaired people
OL,8,Ffeel safer, while also making it
OL,9,Feasier for more people to engage with
OL,10,Fthe police.
OL,12,FTerri said: "I think it's about making
OL,13,Fit easier for people to engage, which
OL,14,Fnot only helps blind and partially
OL,15,Fsighted people but also helps the
OL,16,Fofficers carry out their job.
OL,18,F"Answering the door and not knowing
OL,19,Fwho it is can be quite scary,
OL,20,Fparticularly if it's someone claiming
OL,21,Fto be a police officer."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
