OL,3,CMore protection for blind people from
OL,4,Cpolice impersonators
OL,6,FFor Colin, the protocol means he has
OL,7,Fone less worry when he hears that
OL,8,Fknock at the door.
OL,10,FHe said: "It definitely ensures the
OL,11,Fsafety of visually impaired people. It
OL,12,Fmakes everything safer and everyone
OL,13,Fhappy."
